article.description: — Jaylin Sellers had 17 points in Ball State's 58-54 victory against Georgia Southern on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Sellers scores 17 as Ball State beats Georgia Southern 58-54
article.linkText: Sellers scores 17 as Ball State beats Georgia Southern 58-54
article.story:
MUNCIE, Ind. -- — Jaylin Sellers had 17 points in Ball State's 58-54 victory against Georgia Southern on Wednesday night.

Sellers also contributed seven rebounds for the Cardinals (8-4). Basheer Jihad and Jarron Coleman scored 12 points each.

Carlos Curry finished with 13 points, 11 rebounds and two steals for the Eagles (7-6). Tai Strickland added 13 points and three steals for Georgia Southern.
